.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, daisy, lily, iris
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, april, august, february, june
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, train, airplane, subway, taxi
5 different games are played: canasta, whist, chess, go, domino
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, videographer, manager, police-officer, security-guard

1. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who growsrose
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the designer
3. the person playing canasta is the person who growsballoon-flower
4. the person who's birthday is in august is the person playing whist
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is to the right of the person who growsdaisy
6. the person driving the motorbike is the security-guard
7. the person driving the train is the person who growslily
8. the person playing chess is in the middle
9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the videographer
11. the person driving the train is to the left or right of the police-officer
12. the person driving the subway is the person playing go
13. the person who's birthday is in june is the person driving the taxi
14. the person who's birthday is in february is to the left or right of the person who growsiris

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Birthday	|   february	|    august	|     january	|    april	|    june	|
| Flower		|    lily	|      iris	|      rose	|     daisy	|     balloon-flower	|
| Game	|     domino	|      whist	|      chess	| go	|     canasta	|
| Transport		|     train	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| subway	|   parliament	|
| Job		|     videographer	|     police-officer	|     security-guard	|     designer	|     manager	|
